libs.name: Walmart Shopping
libs.text: Come {Verb} at WALMART, where you`ll receive {Adjective} discounts on all of your favorite brand name {Plural Noun}. Our {Adjective} and {Verb ending with 'ing'} associates are there to {Verb} you {Number} hours a day. Here you will find {Adjective} prices on the {Plural Noun} you need. {Plural Noun} for the moms, {Plural Noun} for the kids and all the latest electronics for the {Type of relative}. So come on down to your {Adjective} {Adjective} WALMART where the {Plural Noun} come first.
